        "type": "regex",
        "pattern": "Authorization[\"'\\s]*[:=][\"'\\s]*Bearer\\s+([A-Za-z0-9+/=_-]{50,200})\\b",
        "message": "Webex OAuth Bearer token detected in Authorization header. Bearer tokens in Authorization headers provide authenticated access to Webex APIs. These headers contain access tokens that grant permissions to user data, messaging, calling, and administrative functions. Exposing Authorization headers with Bearer tokens allows unauthorized API access and potential data breaches. Use secure token storage and avoid hardcoding Authorization headers.",
